{"tid":2242751,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[食唔安訓唔落]尋日浪卡搞到考車牌筆試冇左, 打去運輸署叫番去等收信等消息","createTime":"2020-10-14T08:42:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-14T10:20:04.000Z","uid":24061,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fbaa46938235fba086ab0b48b05cec19076826cc","tid":2242751,"uid":24061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:42:03.000Z","msg":"雖然尋日大家有個打風假應該好開心.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我撞正尋日13/10 考車牌筆試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 咁就取消左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 我打去運輸署問幾時可以考番,<br />\n佢就叫我番去等收信等消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲串串貢講今日我地先打風後第一日番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我已經等左三個月先可以考筆試, 如果再改期既話, 我路試一樣遙遙無期, 加上唔知會唔會有第四波,第五波疫情又搞搞震又延期<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為個筆試我前晚已經食唔安訓唔落<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我仲要蝕左半日AL去考, 依家偷雞唔到蝕渣米<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問下有冇巴絲試過筆試因為惡劣天氣改期, 如果等改期大約要等多幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果三個月又三個月, 因為個筆試要等半年, 我不如以後唔好考算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後, 我真係唔知運輸署同大交合有咩存在既價值, 我真係無野好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f4b14fe0ef41ab989d7d7c63aced6ede8f1198","tid":2242751,"uid":48286,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"筆試都有壓力，你都係放棄考牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d238645e0616a65e49d1f4ef8964db6e3c0655d","tid":2242751,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-14T08:59:24.000Z","msg":"咁你想佢點答你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8786fb9d7d097c68bd3936e5d50da006eb943f4","tid":2242751,"uid":107681,"like"